snippet.title: Car Wars (TI-99/4A) gameplay footage
snippet.description:
Cars Wars is a sort of racing dot eater hybrid. It's a clone of the arcade games Head On by Sega/Gremlin and Crash by Exidy, also cloned by Dodge 'Em on the Atari 2600. You try to collect all the dots and avoid the other car.

I am really bad at this.
